OL,5, Phillip Schofield has quit ITV after   
OL,6, admitting he had an affair with a      
OL,7, younger male ITV employee and lied to  
OL,8, cover it up.                           
OL,10,FThe ex-This Morning host said the      
OL,11,Frelationship with his junior colleague 
OL,12,Fwas "unwise but not illegal".          
OL,14,FIn a statement to the Daily Mail,      
OL,15,FSchofield said he "met the man when he 
OL,16,Fwas a teenager and was asked to help   
OL,17,Fhim to get into television".           
OL,19,FHe apologised for lying to colleagues, 
OL,20,Femployers, the media and public.       
